Cervisiam beertracking This is app is made by students for students!\n\nDo you always want to try new beers and can\'t remember if you drank them already? Or are you a collector and want to drink them all? Or maybe you do it for some bragging rights?\n\nThere is something for everyone in this app!\n--------------------------------\n\nThe name \'Cervisiam\' comes from latin, translated it literally means beer.
